**fy_harbor**
==================
Good day,
The map contains two bases, two warehouses to be precise;located at a harbor. If put alot of time in this map so please give some feedback and rate ! :)

Installation
==================
To install, unpack the .rar file to:

"Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

Comment & Rate
==================  
Please add a comment and rate on my map.
Also tell me if you see any bugs. I'll try to fix them.
